    "## 8. Helpers de Pipeline\n",
    "\n",
    "Fun\u00e7\u00f5es de utilidade para os experimentos: agrega\u00e7\u00e3o multi-seed, persist\u00eancia (com backup timestampado e metadados de hiperpar\u00e2metros), convers\u00e3o JSON-safe das m\u00e9tricas geom\u00e9tricas, e l\u00f3gica de resume (`FORCE_OVERWRITE` flag)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "0c8f0641",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "0c8f0641"
   },
